# Tooltips & Inline Messaging – No Trailing Periods

- **No trailing period** at the end of short tooltips, titles, button labels, and inline helper text.
  - ✅ `Search events by title`
  - ✅ `Show only live events`
  - ❌ `Search events by title.`
  - ❌ `Show only live events.`
- **Keep tooltips concise and imperative**:
  - Prefer short phrases that describe the action or state.
  - Avoid full sentences unless absolutely necessary.
- **Match tone across UI**:
  - Use present tense, neutral/professional voice.
  - Avoid exclamation marks and casual language in production UI copy.

